import { createSvgIcon } from '@mui/material/utils';

export const User = createSvgIcon(
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
    fill="currentColor"
  >
    <path
      fillRule="evenodd"
      d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z"
      clipRule="evenodd"
    />
  </svg>,
  'User'
);
